App name: Parkour Spots

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Basic idea:
Map where users can store parkour spots and see other stored spots.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Spots:
Contains: Name, description, photo.
Could also contain: Difficult level (1-5), Good for, Number of people, Ground material, Video

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Action bar:
*Search spot name
*Filer by (difficulty, good for, etc.)

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
User:
*User can login (using facebook?)
*Edit profile, photo, skills etc (?)

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Code:
*Google Maps API using GPS
*MySQL server - need a raspberry pi!
*Classes for Map, Marker, Spot, User,
*User takes photo with Camera

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
